#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "aRts"
msgstr "aRts"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sound framework in &kde; 2 and 3. Its single-tasking nature caused "
"problems when two sources of sound were encountered. In the &plasma; desktop "
"it is replaced by Phonon.&newpara; More info:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ARts\"&linkmid; Wikipedia: ARts&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"El marc de so en el &kde; 2 i 3. La seva naturalesa tasca-simple ha causat "
"problemes quan es trobaven dues fonts de so. A l'escriptori &plasma; se "
"substitueix per Phonon.&newpara; Més informació:&newpara; &linkstart;"
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ARts\"&linkmid;Viquipèdia: ARts&linkend;"

#. Tag: glossdef
