#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "D-Bus"
msgstr "D-Bus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"D-Bus or Desktop Bus is an inter-service messaging system. Developed by "
"&RedHat;, it was heavily influenced by &kde; 3 DCOP, which it supersedes. "
"Most POSIX operating systems support D-Bus, and a port for Windows exists. "
"It is used by Qt 4 and GNOME.&newpara; More info:&newpara; &linkstart;"
"\"https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/dbus/\"&linkmid;FreeDesktop.org: "
"What is D-Bus?&linkend;&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"D-Bus\"&linkmid;Wikipedia: D-Bus&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"D-Bus o Desktop Bus és un sistema de missatges de servei-intern. "
"Desenvolupat per &RedHat;, que va ser fortament influenciat pel DCOP de "
"&kde; 3, al que substitueix. La majoria de sistemes operatius POSIX suporten "
"D-Bus, i existeix un port per a Windows. És usat per Qt 4 i GNOME.&newpara; "
"Més informació:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/"
"dbus/\"&linkmid;FreeDesktop.org: What is D-Bus?&linkend;&newpara; &linkstart;"
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D-Bus\"&linkmid;Viquipèdia: D-Bus&linkend;"

